  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink265-kilavi">parattai yiṭattāṉ āka voḻukukiṉṟa talaimakaṉ viṭutta vāyiṉ mākkaṭkut talaimakaḷ colliyatu.
          </p>
        <p xml:lang="en">What the heroine told the mediator people sent by the hero who kept being at the place of the concubine.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink265">
<l>pulikol peṇpāṟ pūvarik kuruḷai</l>
<l>vaḷaiveṇ maruppiṟ kēḻal purakkuṅ</l>
<l>kuṉṟukeḻu nāṭaṉ maṟantaṉaṉ</l>
<l>poṉpōṟ putalvaṉō ṭeṉṉīt tōṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>The man from the land of hills</l>
        <l>where a boar, with curved white tusks,</l>
        <l>protects a piglet with beautiful stripes,</l>
        <l>because its female was killed by a tiger—</l>
        <l rend="space">he has forgotten me,</l>
        <l>leaving me with my son, [precious] as gold.</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
